# Example 1 — Task Manager API orchestration
# Usage: marksync shell --script examples/1/orchestrate.msdsl

AGENT editor-1 editor --model qwen2.5-coder:7b --auto-edit
AGENT reviewer-1 reviewer --model qwen2.5-coder:7b
AGENT deployer-1 deployer
AGENT monitor-1 monitor

PIPE review-flow editor-1 -> reviewer-1
PIPE deploy-flow editor-1 -> reviewer-1 -> deployer-1

ROUTE markpact:file=* -> editor-1
ROUTE markpact:deps -> reviewer-1
ROUTE markpact:run -> deployer-1
